=== 意外過世 ===
終極戰士於2014年4月8日過世。他於4月5日入選世界摔角娛樂名人堂，於4月6日出現年度摔角盛会[[摔角狂熱XXX|摔角狂熱XXX]]，於4月7日在[[WWE_Raw|WWE Raw]]進行睽違18年的亮相。<ref name="death">{{cite web|title=Ultimate Warrior passes away|url=http://www.wwe.com/inside/ultimate-warrior-passes-away-26223975|publisher=WWE|access-date=2014-04-15|archive-date=2014-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141109111045/http://www.wwe.com/inside/ultimate-warrior-passes-away-26223975|dead-url=no}}</ref>據報導，在下午五點五十分（[[太平洋時區|PDT]]），終極戰士正當與妻子在[[亞利桑那州|亞利桑那州]]的飯店外面準備上車時暈倒，被送往醫院后不治身亡。<ref>{{cite web|title=Warrior news: Report - Ultimate Warrior initial Cause of Death|url=http://pwtorch.com/artman2/publish/WWE_News_3/article_77608.shtml|work=Pro Wrestling Torch|accessdate=April 9, 2014|archive-date=2014-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140411172840/http://pwtorch.com/artman2/publish/WWE_News_3/article_77608.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

驗屍结果显示終極戰士死於心臟疾病。<ref>{{cite web|title=Warrior had cardiovascular disease|url=http://espn.go.com/espn/story/_/id/10782037/ultimate-warrior-died-cardiovascular-disease|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|accessdate=15 April 2014|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304023941/http://espn.go.com/espn/story/_/id/10782037/ultimate-warrior-died-cardiovascular-disease|dead-url=no}}</ref> 終極戰士的家族有心臟病史，他的父親於57歲過世，而他的祖父的於52歲過世。<ref>{{cite web|last=Caldwell|first=James|title=Breaking WWE news: Ultimate Warrior cause of death|url=http://pwtorch.com/artman2/publish/WWE_News_3/article_77724.shtml|work=Pro Wrestling Torch|accessdate=15 April 2014|archive-date=2019-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031071051/https://www.pwtorch.com/artman2/publish/WWE_News_3/article_77724.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

另據報導，在“摔角狂熱XXX”後台的人員指出終極戰士似乎是持續性的作痛，並指出終極戰士看起來吃力，很不舒服。他們還注意到，終極戰士在WWE Raw表演他搖晃擂台頂繩的招牌動作時看起來非常的虛弱。一位消息人士指出：我們都覺得他看起來很暴躁，這是顯而易見的。（We all felt like he looked like he was going to blow a gasket. It was pretty easy to see.）<ref>{{cite web|title=WARRIOR NEWS: Report - Warrior appeared to be "very sick" prior to death, Hall of Fame special includes Warrior message, Jim Ross blogs on Warrior's legacy|url=http://pwtorch.com/artman2/publish/WWE_News_3/article_77620.shtml|work=Pro Wrestling Torch|accessdate=April 9, 2014|archive-date=2014-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140412114151/http://pwtorch.com/artman2/publish/WWE_News_3/article_77620.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

